(6, 7, '2015-07-13 17:16:13', '2015-07-13 17:16:13', '[vc_row section="yes" full_height="yes" parallax_bg_width="110" full_width="yes"][vc_column width="1/1" animate="fade" animate_delay="0.2"][rev_slider_vc alias="home"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row parallax_bg_width="110" section="yes"][vc_column width="1/3" animate_delay="0.2"][vc_custom_heading text="Inove" font_container="tag:h2|text_align:center|color:%231c613f" google_fonts="font_family:Open%20Sans%20Condensed%3A300%2C300italic%2C700|font_style:700%20bold%20regular%3A700%3Anormal"][vc_single_image image="230" align="center" img_size="full" animate="afc" animate_delay="0.2"][vc_column_text]\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">Um novo conceito em soluções industrias traz consigo não somente maior desempenho como também inúmeros valores agregados. Por que não usá-lo?</p>\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column width="1/3"][vc_custom_heading text="Aprove" font_container="tag:h2|text_align:center|color:%231c613f" google_fonts="font_family:Open%20Sans%20Condensed%3A300%2C300italic%2C700|font_style:700%20bold%20regular%3A700%3Anormal"][vc_single_image image="231" align="center" img_size="full" animate="afc" animate_delay="0.2"][vc_column_text]\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">Utilizando a linha de produtos Hg você ira experimentar o melhor custo beneficio uma vez que buscamos otimizar os processos industriais trazendo com a marca vantagens a curto médio e longo prazo.</p>\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column width="1/3"][vc_custom_heading text="Decida" font_container="tag:h2|text_align:center|color:%231c613f" google_fonts="font_family:Open%20Sans%20Condensed%3A300%2C300italic%2C700|font_style:700%20bold%20regular%3A700%3Anormal"][vc_single_image image="232" align="center" i<a href="http://hagnossq.com.br/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/Hagnos-Site-Juninho-Fino-.jpg" rel="attachment wp-att-288"><img class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-288" src="http://hagnossq.com.br/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/Hagnos-Site-Juninho-Fino--300x200.jpg" alt="Hagnos Site Juninho Fino !" width="300" height="200" /></a>mg_size="full" animate="afc" animate_delay="0.2"][vc_column_text]\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">Ouse, escolha otimizar seus processos, opte por um novo conceito , decida trabalhar com a Hagnos Soluções Químicas.</p>\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row section="yes" img="184" parallax="still" parallax_bg_width="110" overlay="black_20" background="primary"][vc_column width="1/2"][vc_empty_space height="32px"][/vc_column][vc_column width="1/2"][vc_custom_heading text="Solicite a visita de um\r\nrepresentante Hagnos" font_container="tag:h2|font_size:50|text_align:center" google_fonts="font_family:Open%20Sans%20Condensed%3A300%2C300italic%2C700|font_style:300%20light%20regular%3A300%3Anormal"][vc_separator type="short" size="small"][vc_button text="Representantes" type="primary" align="center" url="http://hagnossq.com.br/representantes/"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column width="1/1"][vc_custom_heading text="ALGUNS DE NOSSOS CLIENTES" font_container="tag:h2|text_align:center|color:%231c613f" google_fonts="font_family:Open%20Sans%20Condensed%3A300%2C300italic%2C700|font_style:700%20bold%20regular%3A700%3Anormal"][vc_clients auto_scroll="yes" interval="1" arrows="yes" columns="5" indents="yes"][/vc_column][/vc_row]', 'Home', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'home', '', '', '2018-01-13 14:23:29', '2018-01-13 14:23:29', '', 0, 'http://hagnossq.com.br/?page_id=6', 0, 'page', '', 0),
